///// windows ///////////////////////////////////////////////

- install python (https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.9.1/python-3.9.1-amd64.exe)
- install java (https://javadl.oracle.com/webapps/download/AutoDL?BundleId=243737_61ae65e088624f5aaa0b1d2d801acb16)
- download portable chrome (https://chromium.woolyss.com/), extract to Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/chrome and run setup
- download repository (https://github.com/bartol/amadeus2.hr/archive/master.zip)
- extract repository/dashboard to Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/code
- cd in code dir and run C:\> python -m venv venv and C:\> venv\Scripts\activate.bat
- download and install wheel for psutil (https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/21/71/33cb528381c443df1ee25cbb451da975421bddb5099b11e7f2eb3fc90d6d/psutil-5.8.0-cp39-cp39-win_amd64.whl)
- C:\> pip install -r requirements.txt
- edit config.ini file, edit win/gui.bat, win/update.bat
- create Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/data, Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/cache, Desktop/amadeus-dashboard/logs/{update,gui}
- create shortcut to gui.bat, update.bat on Desktop
- add update.bat to task scheduler (every 30 mins)
